                            <div style="display:inline-flex">
                                <div><h6 style="border-radius:100%;border:5px solid;color:#e15049;width:2%;"></h6></div>&nbsp;
                                <div><h6>To Accelerate Professional growth through Mentoring,Coaching,Innovative knowledge channels & games.</h6></div>
